<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>알릭스 제너러스 (Alix Generous)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/alix_generous_how_i_learned_to_communicate_my_inner_life_with_asperger_s?language=ko' lang='ko'>
아스퍼거 증후군인 내면 세계와 소통할 수 있게 된 방법
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Aug 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Inspiring, Courageous
</span>
</span>
